<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Aqua Project Engine | Build Projects with AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Aqua Project Engine by Aquiplex helps you build websites, apps, and projects using AI. Turn ideas into real outputs instantly.">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #020617;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 48px);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3vw, 18px);
      color: #94a3b8;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      color: white;
      padding: 13px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .cta-btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    /* ── Sections ── */
    .section {
      margin-top: 70px;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 4.5vw, 28px);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .section p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 16px);
    }

    /* ── Grid ── */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #0f172a;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: #6366f1;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3vw, 17px);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    /* ── Steps ── */
    .steps {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .step {
      color: #cbd5f5;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 16px);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      background: #0f172a;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    /* ── Extra link sections ── */
    .link-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 60px auto 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .link-section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 26px);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .link-section p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 30px 16px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 40px 16px;
      }

      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }

      .section[style*="text-align:center"] .cta-btn {
        display: block;
        max-width: 260px;
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .link-section {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("partials/every") %>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Aqua Project Engine</h1>
      <p>
        Turn your ideas into real projects using AI. Build websites, apps, and digital products—
        without coding or complexity.
      </p>
      <a href="/bundles" class="cta-btn">Start Building →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- WHAT IS -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>What is Aqua Project Engine?</h2>
      <p>
        Aqua Project Engine is an AI-powered system developed by Aquiplex that helps users
        transform ideas into structured, real-world projects.
        <br><br>
        Instead of just giving instructions, it generates step-by-step workflows, tools,
        and outputs to help you actually build something.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>What Can You Build?</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>🌐 Websites</h3><p>Create full websites with structure and content.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>📱 Apps</h3><p>Generate ideas and workflows for applications.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🎥 Content Systems</h3><p>Build YouTube channels, Instagram strategies, and more.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🚀 Startup MVPs</h3><p>Turn your startup idea into a working plan.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🎨 Creative Projects</h3><p>Generate thumbnails, visuals, and media workflows.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>📚 Learning Paths</h3><p>Structured plans for coding, AI, and more.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">1. Enter your idea or goal</div>
        <div class="step">2. Define your project type and audience</div>
        <div class="step">3. Aqua generates a structured plan</div>
        <div class="step">4. Use tools and steps to build your project</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHY DIFFERENT -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Why Aqua Project Engine is Different</h2>
      <p>
        Most AI tools give answers. Aqua Project Engine focuses on <span class="highlight">execution</span>.
        It guides you step-by-step and helps you actually complete projects.
      </p>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>Execution Focused</h3><p>Not just ideas—real workflows and outputs.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Step-by-Step Guidance</h3><p>Structured plans that are easy to follow.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>AI-Powered Tools</h3><p>Integrated tools for building faster.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- USE CASES -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Who is it For?</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>Students</h3><p>Learn by building real projects.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Creators</h3><p>Grow content and build systems.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Developers</h3><p>Speed up workflows and prototyping.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Entrepreneurs</h3><p>Build MVPs and launch ideas faster.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FINAL CTA -->
    <div class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Start Building Your First Project</h2>
      <p>Turn your ideas into reality using AI.</p>
      <a href="/bundles" class="cta-btn">Launch Project Engine →</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="link-section">
    <h2>Powered by Aqua AI</h2>
    <p>Aqua Project Engine works seamlessly with Aqua AI to generate ideas, content, and structured workflows.</p>
    <a href="/aqua-ai" class="cta-btn">Try Aqua AI →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="link-section">
    <h2>Learn More About Aquiplex</h2>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-btn">About Aquiplex →</a>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
